ht up with th=\r\ne concept of japa. Japa which deals with the Air element which is unstable =\r\nanyway can cause serious instability in these people.&lt;br&gt;\n&gt; &gt;Some&nbs=\r\np;of the&nbsp;people who have Kundalini &quot;rises&quot; may be people who may feel =\r\nthat they haven&#39;t done a single worthwhile thing in their lives and think t=\r\nhat the faking of Kundalini rises may help them get some esteem in the eye =\r\nof the general public.&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;\n&gt; &gt;Coming to the specific problem:In=\r\n general, for any doctor, the separation of the true from the false claims =\r\nmust precede any attempt at helping the patient. A true Kundalini rise need=\r\ns niyama to finish Vata. Vata tends to like irregularity, in food habits, s=\r\nleeping habits, sexual matters, travel.&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;\n&gt; &gt;To finish Vata, =\r\nall&nbsp;that must be regimentalised, then appropriate herbs used. Control =\r\nof Apana is essential as is Bramhacharya. Application of oils to the body t=\r\no totally calm Vata may be useful. I suppose even Shiro basti in difficult =\r\nreal cases may be useful.&lt;br&gt;\n&gt; &gt;Then institute small&nbsp;Homas to M=\r\nahaGanapati and the nava grahas to be performed by the patient. That should=\r\n really improve matters, as Ganesha is The Lord of the Muladhara.&lt;br&gt;\n&gt; =\r\n&gt;The whole process may be chalked out over one-two years.&lt;br&gt;\n&gt; &gt;I=\r\nn pure non real cases, just psychotherapy may be sufficient.&lt;br&gt;\n&gt; &gt;&lt;=\r\nbr&gt;\n&gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt;\n&gt; &gt;Jai Shree Rama&lt;br&gt;\n&gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt;\n&gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt;\n&=\r\ngt; &gt;&lt;br&gt;\n&gt; &gt;Jai Shree Rama&lt;br&gt;\n&gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt;\n&gt; &gt;On Friday, =\r\nMarch 1, 2013, Narasimha P.V.R. Rao  wrote:&lt;br&gt;\n&gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt;\n&gt; &gt;Nama=\r\nste friends,&lt;br&gt;\n&gt; &gt;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;\n&gt; &gt;&gt;Someone with psychiat=\r\nric problems may expereience what sounds like a Kundalini rise, but it may 